ai.model

Class EnvironmentModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • ai.model.EnvironmentModel

  • public class EnvironmentModel
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the main model object. It must be initialised with list of percepts as well as a list of commands executed. The lists can be empty, but must be provided. This model is passed to AIComponents one by one, which use the information in the percepts to add more information back in to the model. Most of the methods are simple setters and getters, and thus are not commented. Some methods contain some simple logic, the purpose of which is given in comments below.
